  schema:name "Convergent Enrichment" ;
  schema:description "A task prioritization strategy for bootstrapping a self-describing system: enrich from the bottom (foundational vocabulary) and the top (operational context) simultaneously, letting the two fronts converge in the middle where most work happens." ;
